Nigerian tailors and the popular myth that most of them would not make heaven due to how they dissapoint their customers.”  Here’s a classic example of what a Nigerian lady ordered and what was eventually delivered to her.”  The lady took to Twitter to show her dissapointment, saying, her sunday is ruined..    See photo of what she wanted below;    And here’s what she got.   She went further, explaining that she decided to try out a new tailor based on favourable review only for her to end up disspaointed. In her words, “Moral of this story: DO NOT CHEAT ON YOUR TAILOR. I accept the fact that I’m to blame. I listened to praises sang about this tailor  In truth, I my cheat again. Everybody loves to slay.” 